{"tid":610041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首十一月財政盈餘已逾1700億　陳茂波估全年1380億　政府稱三月將現赤字","createTime":"2018-03-29T14:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T00:17:30.000Z","uid":127988,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7816d5bb3664802764cb063b304199afef63309f","tid":610041,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波在本年2月底發表2018/19年度財政預算案，估計2017/18年度（截至今年3月底止）財政盈餘為1380億元。不過，政府今日（29日）公布本財政年度首十一個月的財務狀況，至2月底財政盈餘已達到1724億元。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波早前宣讀本屆政府第一份財政預算案，預料2017/18年度的財政盈餘高達 1,380 億元，較去年原先預算相差 1,217 億元，令社會嘩然。<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，政府今日公布，2月份的財政盈餘是72億港元，首十一個月累積盈餘增至1,724億港元。本財政年度首十一個月的整體開支為4,210億港元，收入為5,934億港元，</span><br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，三月的開支預期將超過收入，令該月出現赤字，累積盈餘將會減少。<br />\n<br />\n不過，早於財政預算案公佈當日，有分析質疑，財政預算案$1380 億盈餘或是報細數，政府的最終盈餘仍有可能逾$1500億。財經事務及庫務局當日回覆《立場新聞》時表示：<br />\n<br />\n本財政年度的大部分主要收入(如地價收入、利得稅和薪俸稅)均已收取。計及餘下兩個月預期的收入和開支，預計二零一七至一八財政年度的盈餘將會下降至1,380億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%96%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E7%9B%88%E9%A4%98%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%BE1700%E5%84%84-%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E4%BC%B0%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B41380%E5%84%84-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%87%E7%8F%BE%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%259B%2588%25E9%25A4%2598%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2580%25BE1700%25E5%2584%2584-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B41380%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%2F&d=fQOv7zOkaCBnn8N6nq7nav9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=69fbff62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%259B%2588%25E9%25A4%2598%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2580%25BE1700%25E5%2584%2584-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B41380%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%2F&h=dcc6dd78\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%96%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E7%9B%88%E9%A4%98%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%BE1700%E5%84%84-%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E4%BC%B0%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B41380%E5%84%84-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%87%E7%8F%BE%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n屌埋單成1700億, 仲話有赤字, 比人貪晒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00560f905dbfa690b14eaa7a4ff8eb719902fbf8","tid":610041,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"香港政府只係為共產黨服務, 香港人你死你事"},{"pid":"7c19be7725e1b64f7b4a4c349f06ce28973ea04e","tid":610041,"uid":3241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"而家講到公共財政都要賺錢咁款<br />\n美國俄國英國赤左幾萬億都未倒台"},{"pid":"9af6004c3343736f2bf1d93b19d9116679c63e97","tid":610041,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"佢好意思講赤字<br />\n一講番條數我怕佢講到一半就唔敢再講點解會赤字"},{"pid":"e950d239c7caf9e22f2573c38975dcc5bd86286f","tid":610041,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c19be7725e1b64f7b4a4c349f06ce28973ea04e","tid":610041,"uid":3241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"而家講到公共財政都要賺錢咁款<br />\n美國俄國英國赤左幾萬億都未倒台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"有核國家邊有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9baa8200df00f53fec00ffb0379b2022a1ffb4","tid":610041,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"p